outputs.output_descr: The project will help Kiribati evaluate existing information on the status, trends, and existing needs for biodiversity conservation; identify and analyse options to fulfil biodiversity obligations; plan and prepare a strategy and plan; prepare national reports; and build capacity for establishment of a clearing house mechanism.

project_descr: The project enables the design of effective response measures to improve Kiribati's efforts in conserving biological diversity at national, sub-national and community levels.
project_title: Kiribati National Biodiversity Strategy & Action Plan
